<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="decide-v">decide <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'saɪd/    美 /dɪ'saɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>决定；选定：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s difficult to <strong>decide between</strong> the two. 
两者之间难以取舍。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s the people who decide the fate of mankind. 
决定人类命运的还是人类自身。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>decided against</strong> going on a holiday abroad for lack of money.  
因为缺钱，我们决定不去国外度假了。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>decide (wh-) to do:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I can’t decide which to choose. 
我不能决定选哪个。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With this unshakable belief, I, at fourteen, decided to become a writer. 
有了这种不可动摇的信念，我在14岁的时候决定成为一名作家。</p><footer> 2010 四川</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>decide + that / wh- 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This last game will decide who is to be the champion.
最后一局将决定谁是冠军。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="decide-on-upon">decide on / upon</h3>
<p>1.<strong>决定；选定：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Have you decided on a date for the wedding?
你们定好婚礼日期了吗？</p></div></div>